nd-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;移动电话：13888384509 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 15198862744&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-margin-before:0em;-webkit-margin-after:0em;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;　一个人一生有三分之一的时间，甚至是更多的时间，是在卧室中度过的，所以卧室的环境好坏，直接关系到一个人甚至是一家人的健康与运气。在家居风水中，卧室，是最重要的一个环节，可以说是整个房子的中心所在，卧室环境的好坏，直接影响整个家庭的运气。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　那么卧室在风水布局中有哪些禁忌呢？\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;禁忌一：卧室的面积太大&quot; src=&quot;http://i0.sinaimg.cn/ast/2012/0426/U7132P54DT20120426140131.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;img_descr&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;禁忌一：卧室的面积太大&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;1、卧室的面积太大&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　一般卧室居住的面积，最适合的是二十平方左右，大于二十平方，则略显阔大。风水上认为房子过大而人少，不利主人居住。这样长久住下去，人的健康和运气就会受到一定的影响。因此，卧室一定不要过大，不要大于二十平米，十到二十平米之间就可以了，如果过大，可以在床上设帐子。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;禁忌2：电器太多&quot; src=&quot;http://i1.sinaimg.cn/ast/2012/0426/U7132P54DT20120426140154.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;img_descr&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;禁忌2：电器太多&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;2、电器过多&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　卧室是休息的地方，需要清净明亮为好。不必要的东西，尽量不要放在卧室，特别是电器太多，会干扰卧室的磁场。电器在风水上被为“火煞”，容易让人烦躁不安或冲动，经常吵闹不休，或者是睡眠不好，容易对人的性格和精神产生影响。同时，抛开风水不说，电器是有辐射的，所以发出的磁场，会长久的慢慢的影响你的身心健康和运气。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;禁忌3：吊灯太长或造型古怪&quot; src=&quot;http://i3.sinaimg.cn/ast/2012/0426/U7132P54DT20120426140237.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;img_descr&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;禁忌3：吊灯太长或造型古怪&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;3、吊灯太长或造型古怪&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　吊灯，做为卧室中必不可少的一个装饰，却成为风水上的一种禁忌。吊灯肯定是安放在卧室的天花板正中央，由于卧室的空间有限，基本上吊灯会压着床的中部和尾部，而这种吊灯压床和梁压床，实际上没有多大区别了，有时候还比梁压床更严重。所以，为了家人的健康和运气，最好是用那种简单的长方形、正方形或圆形的普通吊灯。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;禁忌4：卧室内养花、养鱼&quot; src=&quot;http://i1.sinaimg.cn/ast/2012/0426/U7132P54DT20120426140321.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;img_descr&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;禁忌4：卧室内养花、养鱼&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;4、卧室内养花、养鱼&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　卧室内是不可以养花、养鱼的。轻则影响睡眠质量以及身体抵抗能力，重则招惹桃花和口舌是非。因为花草在风水学上属阴性，会吸收光线，开花的植物尤其不适合在卧室里养。养鱼也是如此，普通人会觉得养鱼能聚财，但卧室并不是聚财的地方，所以在卧室中养鱼不但不会带来财运，还会影响主人休息，进而影响财运和健康。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;禁忌5:床单、床罩的颜色过亮过暗&quot; src=&quot;http://i1.sinaimg.cn/ast/2012/0426/U7132P54DT20120426140352.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;img_descr&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;禁忌5:床单、床罩的颜色过亮过暗&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;5、床单、床罩的颜色过亮过暗&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		　　床单以及床罩的颜色对人的影响是最直接的，因为你睡觉的时候，天天就铺盖这些，这些颜色的能量可以直接作用到你个人的身上去，对健康和运气有直接的影响。比如大红色，就是过亮的颜色，红色如同太阳一般，容易让人产生冲动而烦躁不安的感觉。而过暗的颜色，深蓝深紫的一类，也不适合在卧室中使用。卧室中的颜色一般以浅色偏亮一点的为好，如果能根据八字的五行喜忌，选择卧室的颜色为佳。比如八字喜火，你可以选择粉色一类的浅色系，或者是一些碎花的点缀组合都可以的，但哪怕你五行喜火，也不可以选个大红色，要真的喜欢红色，可以多穿红色的衣服即可。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;禁忌6：床头靠窗户&quot; src=&quot;http://i2.sinaimg.cn/ast/2012/0426/U7132P54DT20120426140416.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap: